1046
01:13:05,910 --> 01:13:17,230
Scott: I think with the biggest development that's recent is that the remote controls, which used to have shit tons of buttons on them and sometimes still do, have had way less buttons on them because all of our televisions now have software in them.

1047
01:13:17,310 --> 01:13:20,610
